          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2462Step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped courgette</strong> and <strong>orzo</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat everything in the oil</p><p>Add the <strong>beef stock</strong> with the <strong>tomato frito</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 5,
